{
  "id": "adv_event_2501_01_04",
  "title": "すみれの\nマラソン\nチャレンジ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう……ルート間違えちゃったかも\n全然気付かなかった……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do I do… I didn’t notice\nI took the wrong route at all…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.6055103302000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.7988435109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "来た道を戻れない？\nそうすれば元のルートに帰れると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can’t you go back the way you came?\nThen you should be able to return to the original course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7988435109,
      "endTime": 11.9404081662,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11601.1564891
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.1337413947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そっか。確かに！　い、急いで戻りまーす！\nえへへ、うっかりミスで思わぬタイムロス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right. That’s true! I—I’ll hurry back!\nEhehe… a careless mistake caused unexpected time loss……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1337413947,
      "endTime": 19.7071428458,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7653.400452900001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7871418476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……ひゃあ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyaah!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7871418476,
      "endTime": 20.7290466308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.8490464846
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみれちゃん……！？\n大丈夫？　思いっきり転んでもうたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sumire-chan…!?\nAre you okay? You took a pretty hard fall…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8490464846,
      "endTime": 26.362583700800002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.5492503483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ……あはは！　だ、大丈夫だよこのぐらい！\nちょっと擦りむいただけだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… ahaha! I-It’s fine‚ really!\nIt’s just a little scrape!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5492503483,
      "endTime": 33.7975952465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.1666655223
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.9909293809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "（いたた……。何やってるんだろ、私……）\n（うっかりして、二人に心配掛けて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Aww… What am I even doing…?）\n（Spacing out and making the two of them worry…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9909293809,
      "endTime": 44.0524936357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.245826721
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "（……だ、ダメダメ！　弱気になっちゃダメ）\n（泣きそうになってる場合じゃ……ない……のに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（N-No‚ no! I can’t lose heart!）\n（This isn’t the time… to cry… but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.245826721,
      "endTime": 52.6137860296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3999996185
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8071193057
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "（中継で繋がってるのに……街頭応援も沢山いるのに）\n（なんでだろう……なんだか凄く……心細いな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even though we’re live… and so many people are cheering out here…）\n（Why… do I feel so… lonely…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8071193057,
      "endTime": 65.5362126667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0999998728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—During Commercial",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.549545733,
      "endTime": 67.5495457211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 67.5495457211
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃん……さっきの大丈夫なんかな、ほんまに\n捻ったり挫いたりしてないやろか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan… is she really okay after that?\nI hope she didn’t twist or sprain anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4495472589,
      "endTime": 76.6648762383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 76.8582093237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "走れてはいるから、大丈夫だと思うけど……\nだいぶペースは落ちてしまってるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s still running‚ so I think she’s okay…\nbut her pace has dropped quite a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8582093237,
      "endTime": 83.23090791679999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 83.4175747552
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "無理してへんかな\nいざとなったら、うちらが掛け合って止めるのも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope she’s not pushing herself too hard…\nIf it comes down to it‚ maybe we should talk to her and stop—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4175747552,
      "endTime": 89.2647854486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 89.4514520961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……いや。それは出来ないし、しない方がいい\nたぶん、すみれが絶対に許さないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No. We can’t‚ and we shouldn’t.\nSumire would never forgive us for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4514520961,
      "endTime": 97.3137198764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 97.520386505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.520386505,
      "endTime": 99.0226495027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.2093161503
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと、考えてたの。なんですみれがいの一番に\nマラソンに挑戦したいって手を上げたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been thinking about it. Why Sumire was the first one\nto raise her hand and volunteer for the marathon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2093161503,
      "endTime": 105.7160508075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9093838929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私達に見せたかったのよ\n一番過酷な企画を、自分一人で成し遂げる姿を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She wanted to show us that\nshe could accomplish the toughest challenge all on her own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9093838929,
      "endTime": 112.7768897294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれはまだ、中学生だからね\n成長期真っ只中の今、無理して故障させたくないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire‚ you’re still a middle schooler.\nIn the middle of your growth‚ I don’t want you to push too hard and get hurt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.963556377,
      "endTime": 122.3515156666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 123.5000017802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、あの時のこととか、子供扱いされたように\n感じてしもうた……ってことなんかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be… because of that time‚ she felt like\nwe were treating her like a kid…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5381825049,
      "endTime": 131.9625363906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 132.1492029429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "そうかもしれない。確かに私達はすみれに対して\n日頃から心配し過ぎることもあったと思うし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe. It’s true we’ve always\nworried too much about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.1492029429,
      "endTime": 139.97337524900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 140.1600418013
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "うちらは当然、対等やと思ってるけど。すみれちゃん\n自身がどう受け取ってたかは、分からへんもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We think of her as equals‚ of course.\nBut we don’t know how she herself felt about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1600418013,
      "endTime": 147.7070486946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
